    "description": "<p>Golden Cafe was established in 1998, starting its business from Food and Beverages, and eventually acquiring couple of coffeeshops and food court over the decade, and intend to further expand its business in the upcoming years with its immense resources</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Currently there are two operating outlet located at Craig Road (Tanjong Pagar) and Katong Shopping Centre, and a Food Factory at Tua Bay Walk. Golden Cafe is a zi char restaurant, which cater home-style cuisine with a vast range of choices and not to mention wallet-friendly options for all customers!&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We have 3 other coffeeshops and other outlets on rent, which we intend to take back once we overcome the manpower crisis. Come join our ranks and help to develop its growth and prosper with us!</p>",
